==Ancient Greek==

===Pronunciation===
*ξηρός / xēros / xay-ros'
=== Etymology ===

*From the base of [[ξέστης]] {{GG|3582}} (through the idea of scorching).

=== Adjective ===
'''ξηρός'''
# [[arid]]; by implication shrunken, earth (as opposed to water): - [[dry]], land, withered.

